      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for reliable transportation. While the engine starts up consistently and the transmission shifts through all gears, the car does show its age with some noticeable exterior blemishes and interior wear. It has been maintained to keep it roadworthy, but a new owner should expect to address some minor cosmetic issues and routine maintenance in the near future. It\u2019s a solid, functional choice for those prioritizing utility over perfection.",
