    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition and has been maintained to the highest possible standards. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition with no signs of wear. Every mechanical component functions perfectly, and the car has a complete service history from the dealership. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer looking for a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory.",
