    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_8_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a car to tinker with? This vehicle is priced to sell and offers a fantastic starting point for someone handy! While it definitely needs some mechanical attention and TLC to get back to its best, it's a great opportunity to own a car at a fraction of the usual cost. Perfect for a hobbyist looking for their next weekend challenge!",
