    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey everyone! \ud83c\udf1f I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, and it's practically spotless inside and out. If you're looking for something that's been truly babied and is ready for a new adventure, this is definitely the one for you. It drives like a dream! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and show it to you!",
      "price": 43500.0,
