    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Offering a concours-level E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS actuation. This specimen boasts a documented service history including a recent valve clearance adjustment and a comprehensive cooling system overhaul. The chassis remains structurally pristine with proactive subframe reinforcement and a factory-spec suspension geometry that preserves BMW's signature 50:50 weight distribution. Power is delivered through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock. The exterior retains its original deep luster, while the interior shows zero bolster compression or UV degradation on the dash. A mechanically synchronized, investment-grade driver\u2019s car.",
